parameters:
\nw[Kuno]There are monsters in this location again... I
wonder if there's something here.

\nw[Rodrigo]Is that so? Well, those monsters weren't anything
special.
\nw[Kuno]I see.

\nw[Kuno]It seems like there won't be any problems going
further in, but since today's objective is the
exam, I'll return here.
\nw[Rodrigo]How did the exam results turn out?

\nw[Kuno]Isn't it fine? You seem to have the strength and
experience to match your appearance, even more so
than me.
\nw[Kuno]For now, it won't become a menial task, right?
\nw[Rodrigo]I see, that will be helpful.

\nw[Kuno]There are monsters here and our small talk is
over. I'll return to the town.
\nw[Rodrigo]Oh.
Now is not the time to leave here.
Now is not the time to leave here.

\nw[Kuno]Look, we've arrived. The exam will start from
here.

\nw[Rodrigo]Well, I consider myself quite a veteran
adventurer, you know.

\nw[Kuno]It's probably an exam for that confirmation. Even
if I join the mercenary group, it would be
troublesome if I'm not useful.

\nw[Kuno]The content of the exam is to battle the monsters
here. Since I'll be fighting together, let's see
if we can coordinate with each other.

\nw[Kuno]Pray said that even if you're too weak, you won't
fail, but at that time, you'll probably be
assigned to menial tasks. The salary is also based
on performance, so it will be low.

\nw[Rodrigo]It's more like an entrance exam, or rather a
confirmation of our abilities. But the examiner is
Kuno, right?
\nw[Kuno]Is there something you want to say?

\nw[Rodrigo]Weren't you expecting a lenient judgment
considering how much we loved each other?
\nw[Kuno]Ah, about us loving each other... that was...

\nw[Kuno]A-anyway, there's no problem with me being the
examiner! I'll be watching closely, so take it
seriously!

\nw[Rodrigo]Alright, then let's recover our magic power
first...

\nw[Kuno]Of course, it's dangerous to recover magic power
in a place where there are no allies and monsters
appear, so that will be deducted points, right?
\nw[Rodrigo]Alright, I got it. I'll do it seriously...
A
